This help page describes how to use templates to export your database in a great variety of formats.  
You can also use templates to customize the BibDesk Services that can be accessed from other applications. 
@ref{Template Preferences} preference help topic. The use of service templates is described in more detail 
in the @ref{System Service} help topic. 

